1125.name: CuAl8Ni6 Tig
1125.Applications: Desalting installations, CuNiAl ship propellers, cladding against corrosion, cladding against wear, gliding surfaces, shipbuilding, pump building, shafts, guide grooves, tube systems etc.
1125.Suitable_For: CuNiAl, CuAlNi, aluminium bronze, ship propellers, 2.0923, Joint welds or building up of aluminum bronze. Cladding (steel) components undergoing metal to metal wear under high pressure. Especially suited for marine environments. The addition of nickel improves corrosion resistance in heated and rough seawater.
